Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.57,0:00:45.59,Chiha-poem,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Impassionate gods have never seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.39,0:00:50.23,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.69,0:00:55.74,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we should hold \Na karuta demo tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:56.95,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.87,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,We'll scare away all the first-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:00.61,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.61,0:01:01.45,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:01.81,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.17,Chiha-main,Desk,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:03.69,Chiha-overlap,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:04.95,Chiha-main,Pork,0000,0000,0000,,They'll run for the hills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.95,0:01:05.87,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:07.29,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:08.92,Chiha-main,Kana,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.35,0:01:10.24,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Taichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.12,0:01:28.31,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Will any new students come?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.76,0:01:30.11,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.32,0:01:35.13,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they fall in love with karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.76,0:01:39.74,Chiha-main,Tai,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.53,0:01:48.29,Chiha-main,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,The way we did...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.57,0:01:58.53,Chiha-card-TS,,0000,0000,0000,,to set the Tatsuta River ablaze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.60,0:02:18.03,Chiha-title2,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1800)}Chihaya Furu
